mg.mapviewer.graph

Class GGraphTile

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • mg.mapviewer.graph.GGraph
        • mg.mapviewer.graph.GGraphTile

  • public class GGraphTile
extends GGraph
    Represents the GGraph object for a particular tile (in terms of Mapsforge). These tile graph objects are kept in a cache for faster access.
